#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/processing-modules/tone-mapping.md
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"contrast compression\n"
": The contrast compression level of the base layer. A higher compression will make the image fit a lower dynamic range.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/processing-modules/tone-mapping.md
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"spatial extent\n"
": The spatial extent of the bilateral filter. Lower values cause the contrast compression to have stronger effects on image details.\n"
msgstr ""

