#. type: Fenced code block
#: content/preferences-settings/shortcuts.md
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"d=global/no-op\n"
"l=global/no-op\n"
"m=global/no-op\n"
"p=global/no-op\n"
"s=global/no-op\n"
"t=global/no-op\n"
