#. type: Fenced code block
#: content/special-topics/opencl/setting-up.md
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"crw-rw-rw- 1 root root 195,   0 Jul 28 21:13 /dev/nvidia0\n"
"crw-rw-rw- 1 root root 195, 255 Jul 28 21:13 /dev/nvidiactl\n"
